<form @submit.prevent="onSubmit" class="formWrapper">
  <input
    type="text"
    7
    placeholder="To-do..."
    v-model="title"
    class="wrapperElem"
  />
  <timeselector
    :displayFormat="'HH:mm'"
    :returnFormat="'HH:mm'"
    :interval="{ h: 1, m: 5 }"
    v-model="time"
    :placeholder="'DL'"
    :required="true"
    :displaySeconds="false"
    class="wrapperElem"
  ></timeselector>
  <button class="add" type="submit">
    +
  </button>
</form>
